text: Elisa Lohmann (born 22 July 1998 Flörsheim) is a German volleyball player. == Career == She participated in the 2015 FIVB Volleyball Girls' U18 World Championship, and the 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League. == References == == External links == * FIVB profile * https://www.cev.eu/Competition- Area/PlayerDetails.aspx?TeamID=8957&PlayerID;=60451&ID;=757 * https://www.schweriner-sc.com/mannschaft/1-liga-saison-201718/ Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:German women's volleyball players Category:People from Main-Taunus-Kreis
